Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:38.87,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,The second term starts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to face everyone and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:41.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Bonavuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.46,Narration,Announcer (Yu),0000,0000,0000,,Nice forehead catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.71,Default,Uno,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:49.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:50.21,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.46,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.23,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Bonavuu to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:55.80,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, mativu—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.22,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.55,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.43,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.19,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your message!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.18,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-After the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.93,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(277,97)\c&HFEFFFC&\3c&H453702&\bord2}Takaragi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:07.81,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(237,58)\fs18\an7\c&H000200&\3c&HFFFDFF&\bord3}Hope you feel okay after the championship\NGet lots of rest today\N\N{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFEFFFF&\3c&H453604&\t(946,988,\alpha&H00&)}8/19 (Sat)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:09.37,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You s-sent it right away, \Nbut I replied so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:10.94,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an9\c&HFEFFFF&\3c&H453604&\bord3}Konohoshi here.\N{\alpha&HFF&\t(1237,1279,\alpha&H00&)}Sorry for the lste reply\N{\alpha&HFF&\t(2489,2530,\alpha&H00&)}Madr a typo\N{\alpha&HFF&\t(3239,3281,\alpha&H00&)}R
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,224)\fs18\an7\c&H000200&\3c&HFFFDFF&\bord3}Good morning~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:12.88,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Then I ended up sending \Nway too many stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.94,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\an8\c&H05053B&\3c&HFBFEFB&}Made a mouse-take\N{\c&H92FD58&\3c&H2C2C4B&\bord3\fnArial Black\alpha&HFF&\t(733,774,\alpha&H00&)}I'm sorry...\N{\c&H05053B&\3c&HFBFEFB&\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\alpha&HFF&\t(1734,1775,\alpha&H00&)}Been a while!!\N{\alpha&HFF&\t(2234,2276,\alpha&H00&)}Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.94,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.44,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have lots of cute stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:22.20,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad to see \Nthat you're doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:24.61,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.83,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Konohoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.62,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.66,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Your rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.23,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,The rocketry tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:32.12,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The class prez said she came to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.09,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.13,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.84,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from Emihara-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.58,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san, have you seen Haruno's video?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.79,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.22,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.62,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,She felt compelled to raise her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:50.73,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.66,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.62,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.23,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.48,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.21,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno, you're good at taking videos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.30,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.05,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,How is this thing flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.07,Default,Uno,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.92,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Gunpowder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.18,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Attained altitude: 891 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.75,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,Feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.12,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Around 270 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.82,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san's rocket flew \Nthe highest in the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.84,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make you the winner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.84,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(194,1)\an2\fs40\fnArial Black\c&HB3AC9F&\4c&H827B6C&\bord0.5\shad2.5\t(235,360,\fscy50)\t(694,903,\fscy100)\pos(498,178)}Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.55,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.09,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The one that flies the highest \Nisn't necessarily the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.09,DefaultTop,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize model rockets \Ncould be so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.02,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,It was so, so, {\i1}so{\i0} thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:25.76,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.62,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure \Neveryone knows about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.10,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.30,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.60,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.64,DefaultTop,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Our homework over summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.55,DefaultTop,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.55,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, Sacchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.57,DefaultTop,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your defeat with honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.82,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The Ultra High-Power Dream is a big hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.19,DefaultTop,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks? No, it's a rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.44,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone's watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Haruno's video!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:51.66,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the rocket we made \Ncould have such an impact on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.38,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.57,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel a bit \Nrestless for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:02.31,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, did you get to talk \Nto Emihara-sensei yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.53,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.88,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to go to the teachers' office!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.39,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's a lot of things \NI need to talk to her about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:12.91,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:16.39,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Is Raimon-san not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.33,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, did you see Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:20.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She ambushed me by the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.15,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Ambushed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When I said hello, she suddenly said, \N"Show me your homework!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and took my notebook against my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.79,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pristine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.67,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\c&HA87C76&\3c&HFAEEE7&}Teachers' Office
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.67,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord1\fnComic Sans MS\c&HB08C72&\3c&H70554C&}Teachers' Office
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.53,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get back safe after the championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.67,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.22,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:42.60,Default,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Takaragi and Akeuchi were in \Nsafe hands getting back with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.55,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:48.30,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the ride back was like a funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:53.42,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,They were both dead quiet, and the \Nsilence was positively suffocating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.56,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(274,1)\an6\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&H9C5B24&\3c&HA7A59E&\bord3\fsp7\move(573.5,42,488.5,42,24,1734)}Silent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:05:00.10,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Man, sorry I suck so much at jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.93,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I even say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.91,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.70,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.82,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You really gave it your all \Nfor the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:13.15,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You look better than I thought you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:16.13,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've toughened up \Nduring summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:21.78,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,L-Losing was h-hard and p-painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:26.80,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,B-But thanks to everyone, \NI-I want to give it another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.51,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.22,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:30.79,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Attagirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.26,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Attagirl, Konohoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.77,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H2D3036&\frz-16.91\fax-0.28\pos(340.5,165)}Attendance Roster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.77,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,To be perfectly honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:39.80,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I had myself worried that you might \Nstop coming to school as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.15,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,As well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.99,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Raimon won't be attending \Nschool for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.53,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We got a phone call from \Nher parent this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.69,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.59,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Have you talked about \Nanything with Raimon lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.75,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, n-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.87,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't r-replied to any of my messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.52,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Takaragi said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:06.38,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to reach her \Nsince the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.75,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Raimon-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:15.66,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That tournament meant a lot more \Nthan normal for you and Raimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.02,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Even I could tell that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:22.58,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The pain of losing is just proof \Nof how seriously you took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:28.03,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, only those who have gone through\Nthe same thing can understand that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.17,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:30.78,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.28,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You should know more than \Nanyone how Raimon feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.38,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, you're here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.36,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You came here before she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:44.99,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep doing what I can \Nfor her as her teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.75,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So I want the rest of you, as her friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.30,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,to look after Raimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:54.99,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are things only you \Ncan do, because of all you've faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.06,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That only I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:06:59.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.02,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't yell at you, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.41,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.05,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't flick your forehead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.20,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.90,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what happened to you, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:12.77,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um, S-Sensei said that Raimon-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:13.70,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.03,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:19.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go over to Matataki's place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be real bad if she got held back a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.04,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.31,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Takaragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.16,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The video from the championship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:36.31,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you happen to record my speech as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.56,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.56,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.56,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I want you to s-send it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.06,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.16,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,The bath is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.07,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:55.25,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My... a-awful speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.33,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the rocket thing you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.94,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't realize i-it was this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.11,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.83,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you watching that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.05,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.84,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,The pain from th-that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I need to fully overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.89,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:24.60,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I need to confront m-my failure here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.89,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,or else I can't move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.36,DefaultItalics,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.41,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.36,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have a video of the launch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.49,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this one also make you cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.09,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,No good. She's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.13,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe she's out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.88,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The last time we were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.63,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(155,1)\fs30\fnArial Black\c&H2C4EE3&\frz22.44\c&HF9DEA2&\3c&HFBFFFD&\4c&HFBFFFD&\bord3\shad1\pos(301,106.5)}Clatter clatter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.63,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(155,1)\fs30\fnArial Black\c&H2C4EE3&\frz22.44\3c&H13181D&\4c&H13181D&\bord1\shad0.8\pos(301,106.5)}Clatter clatter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.63,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(273,1)\fscy83.36\t(23,774,\fscy100)\fscx83.36\t(23,774,\fscx100)\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&HF9DEA2&\3c&HFBFFFD&\4c&HFBFFFD&\bord4\shad2\move(489.09,94.52,500.5,58,23,774)}Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.63,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(273,1)\fscy83.36\t(23,774,\fscy100)\fscx83.36\t(23,774,\fscx100)\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&HF9DEA2&\3c&H13181D&\4c&H13181D&\bord2\shad1.2\move(489.09,94.52,500.5,58,23,774)}Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.22,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She forced her way in like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.19,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Matataki we're dealing with here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:08.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She might show up at school \Nbefore you know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,talking about how she got into \Na fight with her old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.03,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:16.65,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,might not come to school ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:24.43,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is, if we don't do something! \NSo we should come back here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.16,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:29.38,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.40,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be going home for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.76,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.47,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takaragi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.97,Narration,Announcer (Yu),0000,0000,0000,,Nice forehead catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.22,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:46.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time really \Nusing foreheadpathy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.51,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.44,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're very good at hiding your own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see it clearly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.74,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The doubts and worries inside your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.02,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That maybe this isn't \Nthe place you should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.63,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.63,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.99,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:17.01,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the first time I've faced this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.78,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I was learning the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,A friend and I made a promise:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:26.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,we'd both do well at an upcoming competition \Nwith the goal of becoming pianists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.22,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We practiced every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.74,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And that, in and of itself, was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:38.31,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,After the competition, \Nshe stopped coming to lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:45.35,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Getting top place or not, \Nwinning or losing, all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, it's scared me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:52.26,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, in order to turn \Na blind eye to that fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:55.40,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I decided all results, no matter what they were, held an equally precious value,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.51,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,and I've held faith \Nin that ideal all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.26,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I fervently hoped that that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:06.44,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,everyone's dream could come true \Nwithout making anyone sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:07.27,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.99,Flashback,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.77,Flashback,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove it by winning that championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.28,Flashback,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:16.15,Flashback,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,there's no reason for me to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:23.16,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down inside, I feared that Matataki-chan\Nmight turn out like that girl I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.69,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:30.16,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Even before the results were out, I was too \Nbusy thinking about what'd happen if we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:34.05,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else dedicated themselves \Nto aiming for the skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.92,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,and here I was, with my half-hearted resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.86,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Yu-chan said, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:44.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared of seeing people hurt \Nas their dreams are shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the true cause of your doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.19,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.19,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,They're not shattered yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.65,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, i-it's true that we lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.07,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-We were beaten to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.44,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:04.64,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When I watched the \Nv-video that you recorded,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:09.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got to see how our rocket flew\N with unclouded eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.57,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:16.67,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,When everyone s-said good things \Nabout it, I-I was really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.67,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I managed to feel glad that \Nwe entered the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,L-Losing hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.30,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,H-Having failed hurts so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:32.31,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I felt like I wanted to just disappear, \No-over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.31,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:39.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have room to s-stand back up \Nas many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:43.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I may have messed up, but I can \Njust find firm footing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.37,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was told!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how badly I get beaten to a pulp,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.26,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,there's no reason for me to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.71,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know, the video of my speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.51,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:06.32,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was shocked at how terrible it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:11.55,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks for recording it, \Neven though I sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.56,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.88,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Why, after all that suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.06,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,After that, why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:25.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I... w-want to enter the championship \Nagain with everyone next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.86,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,With you, Akeuchi-san, and Raimon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.33,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:35.46,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to launch a rocket \Nthat we build together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:40.21,Flashback,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,The rocket that you all built was so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.58,Flashback,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,When's the next time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.46,Flashback,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of rocket will you launch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.47,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:49.72,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to do it again too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.87,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:52.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:58.62,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be the first one \Nto discover your own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.72,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Take as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:05.71,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong, Umika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.13,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.01,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:17.62,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I found out j-just how weak \NI am d-during this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.38,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,A magic spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:25.18,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So that some of your strength \Nmay reside in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give you some of my pep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Rub, rub, rub!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.32,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to end up with a chafed forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.39,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some of my fun, I-I-I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.19,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll throw in a batch \Nof my intensity on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.15,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,517)\q2\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H2628EB&\pos(312,-4)\3c&H2628EB&\bord1.5\blur3\fsp0.5}sting    sting    sting    sting    sting    sting
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.15,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,517)\q2\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H2628EB&\pos(312,-4)\3c&H9DC1FF&\bord1.5\fsp0.5}sting    sting    sting    sting    sting    sting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.32,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.62,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like a weight's been lifted off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.29,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I need to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:01.92,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:05.10,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back, Matataki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.20,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:14.86,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying in the dark and come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.06,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:17.38,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.17,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Let's listen to the radio together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.75,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a jazz program on at this—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.19,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.31,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:26.53,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from you, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.44,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Skipped a generation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.80,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.70,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend quit playing the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:39.02,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan always said she \Nwanted to be a great pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:43.58,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known this would happen, \NI wouldn't have tried so hard at the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.72,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I stole her dream from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:52.59,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this stupid dream of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:57.74,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up on your dreams \Ncan happen to anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.60,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,as sad as it might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.00,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.60,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.88,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a bit vain of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.73,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,You should be a little more modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.08,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,It's happened to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.99,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I've given up on a dream or two in my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.73,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.12,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.62,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,And in my shame, I hid it away \Nhere in this lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.88,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't made it {\i1}that{\i0} easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.88,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.63,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:35.76,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up on your dreams is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.89,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.33,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Having dreams, giving up on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.02,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,ruining someone else's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.36,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.81,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.54,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.78,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams aren't something \Nyou force yourself to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.66,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:56.20,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone tells me to find my own dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.56,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,How about you think of it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.79,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to have your own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.12,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to become someone \Nwho can cheer on other people's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.67,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,People with dreams who \Ncan't take that first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:12.63,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,People discouraged after failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.66,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,People who look ready to give up at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.36,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be the one who cheers on \Npeople like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.33,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for the faint of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.93,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be the kindest, most confident,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.56,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,and strongest person of all to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.31,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.87,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Why, of course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:37.03,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I know your kindness has given me \Nplenty of courage, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.37,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.55,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.16,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,Would your gramps lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.91,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.61,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.17,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of person I wanna be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:56.88,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a kind, confident, \Nand, um... cute person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.55,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.07,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,I know that ahead on that path,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.87,Flashback,Haruno's Grandfather,0000,0000,0000,,you'll find something to call your very own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.43,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:11.94,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to become the kind of \Nperson I set out to be back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:17.17,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I do want to become someone \Nwho supports those with dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.69,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to be of any use to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.03,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.54,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sharing in those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.46,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I was powerless to change anything as I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:33.85,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I don't \Nwant to stay the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.12,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Matataki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.72,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:49.48,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.75,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:55.11,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to make rockets with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:55.98,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.24,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sick of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.41,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Class Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.24,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's part of your job or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.18,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,but you really don't need to do this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.75,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Or, well, it's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.54,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Just have fun at your little club without me—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.84,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.42,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.05,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You big dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.82,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy! Dummy! Muddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.76,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go around calling people dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.64,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to the muddy hippos in the jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:26.31,DefaultTop,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.61,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Turning grumpy after losing once...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:31.58,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's so uncool of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.57,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You got so worked up about winning, \Nand you're already giving up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.82,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.58,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,If you're giving up, then I'll make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.95,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take everyone into outer space instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.58,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a way better rocket than you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.57,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,and get our group promoted \Nto a bona fide official club!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.22,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:52.92,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,If I make all that happen, \Nthen you'll have lost big-time to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.69,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll never be able to change that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.03,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting a little differently today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.55,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's the power of my Umika-chan respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:05.18,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you told me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:09.31,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You said I didn't have \Nanything that I really loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.92,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I think you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:16.23,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I was running away from treating anything \Nas dear to me this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.82,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:23.45,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Scared of being caught up in my own dreams \Nand goals and hurting someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:28.79,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I wanted to cheer on \Neveryone else's dreams instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.79,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.65,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do \Ncheering from the stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.29,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be partners in the true sense, \Nworking toward the same goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.83,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,or else you can't share in their frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.08,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,or call out to them when they're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:47.10,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the kind of person I wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.60,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I want to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.03,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can find something to call my own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:56.35,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,and be on equal terms \Nwith everyone—with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.70,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And one day, just like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.83,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be someone who works toward \Na goal and accomplishes something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.24,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't accomplished anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.50,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.41,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.57,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.87,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're throwing out your goggles?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.49,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What's it matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.63,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,They're just junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.86,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:24.84,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.01,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I will, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:29.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I said I didn't \Nhave a single thing I hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.76,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:36.02,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when you act like \Na big loser like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.64,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Me... and everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:39.65,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.65,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So, Matataki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.36,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.16,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.01,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:22:00.21,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as competent at things \Nas you all think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.01,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I can't...
